  Really fix new llvm-config in live ebuild, bug #392715

  13 Dec 2011; Naohiro Aota <naota@gentoo.org> llvm-2.9-r2.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd wrt #320221

  12 Dec 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> llvm-3.0.ebuild,
  llvm-9999.ebuild:
